Unraveling the Secrets of IP Addresses and Subnets 🕵️‍♀️

What's an IP Address, Anyway?

✪ IP Address Fundamentals:

1️⃣  IP addresses consist of a network identifier and a host identifier. 🌐
2️⃣  Each device on a network has a physical (MAC address), logical (IP address), and hostname identity. 🖥️
3️⃣  IP addresses allow network traffic to reach its intended destination. 🎯
#Networking

✪ Subnets:

1️⃣  Subnets are isolated network segments used for security and performance. 🔒
2️⃣  They help control and manage network traffic, enhancing security and performance. 🚀
#Security

